0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T12:05:09.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"e9044b8f8a523b410d9a6bcfd733259aecfd7d0a","tid":421344,"uid":56020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T12:14:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一般影建築物會喺早上或下午3點後影，<br />\n唔會正午影，<br />\n側光就會輪廓突出又夠sharp,<br />\n樓上話用移軸鏡的確係個好選擇，<br />\n可以修正變型,<br />\ncpl gnd瀘鏡會一齊使用。<br />\n<br />\nbtw,連登唔係好多叻仔鍾意教人影相咩？<br />\n一深啲就即刻收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實CPL反而少用<br />\n因為某d建築嘅外場有coating，用左CPL會有奇怪嘅效果"},{"pid":"60c7fe5f617e2bd557115d6436dfeca3e5da2caa","tid":421344,"uid":117044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T12:24:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3cdf10cb10b36bd00c389f275c3fc76e15585bcf","tid":421344,"uid":56020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T13:40:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一般影建築物會喺早上或下午3點後影，<br />\n唔會正午影，<br />\n側光就會輪廓突出又夠sharp,<br />\n樓上話用移軸鏡的確係個好選擇，<br />\n可以修正變型,<br />\ncpl gnd瀘鏡會一齊使用。<br />\n<br />\nbtw,連登唔係好多叻仔鍾意教人影相咩？<br />\n一深啲就即刻收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實CPL反而少用<br />\n因為某d建築嘅外場有coating，用左CPL會有奇怪嘅效果</blockquote><br />\n可以減低玻璃反光嘛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔一定岩用<br />\n<br />\n因為如果有coating，減完光會有奇怪pattern"},{"pid":"17f375addbed58ca78a862b4c0234c96036e9051","tid":421344,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T13:44:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一般影建築物會喺早上或下午3點後影，<br />\n唔會正午影，<br />\n側光就會輪廓突出又夠sharp,<br />\n樓上話用移軸鏡的確係個好選擇，<br />\n可以修正變型,<br />\ncpl gnd瀘鏡會一齊使用。<br />\n<br />\nbtw,連登唔係好多叻仔鍾意教人影相咩？<br />\n一深啲就即刻收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n連登多潛水大師"},{"pid":"1701f6aba853f8ae46644741c3b45ac5599cfbb1","tid":421344,"uid":117044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T13:49:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"47114f4e1beaf05442e22448dca159ba3759b198","tid":421344,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T13:52:50.000Z","msg":"我班fd又比啲疑似攝台招返黎既變態煩鳩搞<br />\n真係後悔當初留低左contact"},{"pid":"14c945e884a58e48d1995516ffd379b3f86fffa1","tid":421344,"uid":389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T13:58:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一般影建築物會喺早上或下午3點後影，<br />\n唔會正午影，<br />\n側光就會輪廓突出又夠sharp,<br />\n樓上話用移軸鏡的確係個好選擇，<br />\n可以修正變型,<br />\ncpl gnd瀘鏡會一齊使用。<br />\n<br />\nbtw,連登唔係好多叻仔鍾意教人影相咩？<br />\n一深啲就即刻收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n連登多潛水大師</blockquote><br />\n多鳩吹大師至真</blockquote><br />\n從來影相就係吹水無敵<br />\n一出作品就預左比啲咀炮大師插到一文不值"},{"pid":"0194983b0d6e7598ea3e028fb8804d440519b231","tid":421344,"uid":145769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T14:01:20.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n<br />\n我用photoshop執<br />\n去十幾件背較不同底"},{"pid":"cbbc9ce26c578c8324386401731456b4bd071fe7","tid":421344,"uid":131064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T14:36:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我班fd又比啲疑似攝台招返黎既變態煩鳩搞<br />\n真係後悔當初留低左contact</blockquote><br />\n今次又邊條傻鳩搞游B呀？偷拍輕熟女果個？"},{"pid":"a0e6d995b01dcb3dc67128d4c818699bfa77cc3a","tid":421344,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T14:59:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我班fd又比啲疑似攝台招返黎既變態煩鳩搞<br />\n真係後悔當初留低左contact</blockquote><br />\n今次又邊條傻鳩搞游B呀？偷拍輕熟女果個？</blockquote><br />\n唔係搞游b<br />\n搞游b我直接套料然後放上公海公審佢啦<br />\n之前有個咩地方的大媽咪聲稱自己成日當面屌游b<br />\n結果比埋機會佢同游b同場較量/認親認戚<br />\n結果咪佢對住游b真身都唔知<br />\n比圍內人笑<br />\n<br />\n亦唔係偷拍輕淑女果個（我估唔係）<br />\n<br />\n係有啲人直接騷擾我啲fd姐"},{"pid":"e508cd582818de9eebf0c2968168f0ed979b18e2","tid":421344,"uid":131064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T15:05:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我班fd又比啲疑似攝台招返黎既變態煩鳩搞<br />\n真係後悔當初留低左contact</blockquote><br />\n今次又邊條傻鳩搞游B呀？偷拍輕熟女果個？</blockquote><br />\n唔係搞游b<br />\n搞游b我直接套料然後放上公海公審佢啦<br />\n之前有個咩地方的大媽咪聲稱自己成日當面屌游b<br />\n結果比埋機會佢同游b同場較量/認親認戚<br />\n結果咪佢對住游b真身都唔知<br />\n比圍內人笑<br />\n<br />\n亦唔係偷拍輕淑女果個（我估唔係）<br />\n<br />\n係有啲人直接騷擾我啲fd姐</blockquote><br />\n私怨野唔賞鯉<br />\n你自己戇鳩怪得邊個"},{"pid":"ea7b0de195decf9d8cd11c76f772783d8fc649ec","tid":421344,"uid":143582,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T05:09:54.000Z","msg":"應該光線構圖先係重點wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec49a535a4786c558c9e4e91966b45d62366bf33","tid":421344,"uid":389,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T05:36:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該光線構圖先係重點wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當年石元泰博既桂離宮堅正<br />\n表達到禪既空寂感<br />\n有人話係包豪斯既簡約性現代性<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/03/133624_d2b87ef099289bdcae73e8dcbb8e8b1c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2F133624_d2b87ef099289bdcae73e8dcbb8e8b1c.jpg&h=cde93df0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/03/133625_d51fad30e01cf9e7d1f56f0b1f76e016.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2F133625_d51fad30e01cf9e7d1f56f0b1f76e016.jpg&h=4e01a634&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/03/133626_d51fad30e01cf9e7d1f56f0b1f76e016.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2F133626_d51fad30e01cf9e7d1f56f0b1f76e016.jpg&h=ad481196&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以上可見單係線條都盡顯功力"},{"pid":"a318cba5e9cc5f0704db5f0424c650d82e527de4","tid":421344,"uid":78887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T13:56:05.000Z","msg":"我覺得光線 對比 同線條是最重要的"}]}